===Transitive verb===
'''to maneuver''' (''[[present participle]]'' [[maneuvering]], ''[[past tense]] and [[past participle]]'' [[maneuvered]])
Also manœuvre (manœuvring, manœuvred), manoeuvre (manoeuvring, manoeuvred).
#To move (something) carefully, and often with difficulty, into a certain position.

